\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Per-batch dataflow. The objective, retrieval chunks, and recent feedback build the LLM prompt. The LLM emits a validated JSON plan that FuzzyVM consumes to bias strategy weights and ban opcodes. goevmlab runs the generated state tests across two EVM clients. Divergences flow back into the next prompt, and repeated zero-divergence batches trigger objective rotation.}}{3}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:arch}{{1}{3}{Per-batch dataflow. The objective, retrieval chunks, and recent feedback build the LLM prompt. The LLM emits a validated JSON plan that FuzzyVM consumes to bias strategy weights and ban opcodes. goevmlab runs the generated state tests across two EVM clients. Divergences flow back into the next prompt, and repeated zero-divergence batches trigger objective rotation}{figure.1}{}}
